<li><b>Decipher</b>. Spend 1 intellect point to examine a piece of writing or code you
do not understand. Make a intellect roll of 3 (or higher, depending on the
code or language). On success, you get the gist of the message. If used
in combat, takes an action.</li>
<li><b>Endurance</b>. Any duration of physical action is halved or doubled. E.g. you can
